Easily the best series I've ever seen, the actors are flawless, the plots are magnificent. Do ignore all the negative reviewers as they are mostly Christian people getting angry be cause Satan this Satan that.... Great series, lots of humor, this series deserves nothing but love. The whole story about Satan being in the human world is just intriguing and mysterious, Episode after episode i want to watch more and more every time. Really entertaining, makes you think, makes you emotional... I can't help but say only good things about this series be cause it is a good series, huge fan here and recommend this to anyone who likes crime, mystery, and some devilish good fun.